summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $115.31, or so much thereof as may be necessary from the Water Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying the city's portion of the 1910 general taxes on certain property in sections 18, 19, 20, 21, 22, 27, 27, 28, 29, 30, 31, 32, 33, 34 and 35, in township 22 north, range 8 east W.M.
